race.comment: SLY BOOTS (4) gripped on late with the 58.5kg when a sound first-up third over 1400m at this track. Returned in good order and can stalk the speed and play a leading role. AMREEKIYAH (12) disappointed at her last two runs and look for a better performance up to the mile with the limit weight. Blinkers go on and will be launching late. HYPERBOLIC (2) progressive mare who keeps raising the bar this time in. Made a mess of them over 1600m at this track and trip at latest. Can get across from the draw and play a leading role again. HIGH BLUE SEA (5) gets a better set-up today after covering ground when a fighting fourth over 1550m at Canterbury. Can run the mile out and race a little closer from the good gate. DANCES WITH HOOVES (9) massive win over the 1400m in the Mudgee Cup. Has an even better record at the mile and not to be overlooked.
